# -*- mode: org; -*-
#+title: CHIP-8.c

A simple chip-8 emulator written in C.

* Dependencies
- standard C libraries
- Autotools
  + ~automake~
  + ~autoconf~

* Building
1. Build system initialisation
   #+begin_src sh
     autoreconf --install            # gen build system files
     ./configure                     # gen Makefiles
   #+end_src
2. Compile the executable with the humble ~make~ command 
3. execute the program with ~./src/chip8 roms/*.ch8~
